es to enjoy the view. If this game continues to be updated, it will be great by the time it reaches full rollout!Note for the devs:I found a few bugs so far I wanted to report-Tab doesnt always pull up pda-Rebalance gun damage-As long as a dino is behind you, it cannot hurt you-when you create a new game it is not truely new, it also doesnt spawn you with anything half the time-When you leave the game and come back, sometimes your secondary weapon is gone.As the game progresses and updates are made I will change my rating and review, I will also have gameplay video up shortly that I will link.Thanks for reading!Edit 12/16/14: The developer contacted me confirming they had recieved my feedback and would be implementing several parts.I will be changing my recommendation to a thumbs up once the first update is out. As long as the devs will listen to the community and continue to put out updates, I will reccomend it. As I continue to play it, I enjoy it more and more. Of it still isnt fully there, but it is an enjoyable time waster. As of now there really is no objective, Im hoping some objective will be added later. Also another thing that I have found to be annoying is the fact that you cant stack  items. If you find a pile of 2 arrows, and one of 3 you cannot combine them. Once again im sure this will be fixed later."
