76561198149690435,Recommended,322920,18381251,"Posted: 8 October, 2015",all,coltcoyote,"After playing this game for  quite some time, its time for me to update my review of it.The graphics and evniroment in the game are very very nice, in fact so much so that I have logged in at times just to get screenshots to use as desktop wallpapers. If you have a machine capable of reliably running this at the hightest settings, do so, its amazing!The gameplay is a mixed bag, there are issues like very low stamina and  lack of being able to swim for even a few feet or climb anything that put a lot of undue hardships on the player and kills what is otherwise a really nice immersion factor.The search for better gear is a bit tedious too and could have been handled a bit better.The actual hunting part of the game is quite enjoyable and is a nice mix of  fun and fear. The multiplayer modes are what you'd expect, PvP and PvE are both playable altho the hosting setup can be a bit buggy at times.The dinosaurs models are all very nice, altho the developers seem to have a feather fetish, and put them on damn near everything.The Dinosaur AI is.....well, OK at best and notably arfy at worst. At their best, the dinosaurs act like you would expect them to, nd its sometimes fun watching them from afar. I've seen a T-Rex seemingly following a heard of Trikes, and watched Utah raptors interacting with each other in a manner that seemed realistc. I would LOVE to see some actual dinosaur on dinosaur predation though, that would add immensly to the gameplay.On the other paw though, the dinosaurs seem to have senses and abilities that defy physics at times, able to climb terrain that they should not be able too, and detect things that they simply should not be able too see/smell/hear at times and be totaly blind to things they should be able to see/smell/hear at others. An animal the size of the quetzalcoatlus (as modeled ingame) should not be able to fly with a man sized object in its claws.They also have supernatural stamina, unlike the player, and can and will run clean across the damn island when wounded. Any animal that bleeds out to a noted point of say below 20% health should not be able to run for any notable distance....EVER!On the whole its still a fun game to play but the asking price is way too high. this is at best, a $20.00 us dollar game. Get it on sale, or part of a bundle and then its worth it.I would reccomend it conditionally, get it on sale, just don't pay full price for it."
