um community shines. So dont be affraid to ask anything.GFx: 9-10SFx: 8-10Gameplay: 7-10 (why cant you JUMP?)Scary YES worth it YES. Recommended all the way. Go for it!.. I still sleep with eyes WIDE open after hearing loud footsteps lol  :)"
