ing but then when I think it is clear a T-Rex will suddenly appear.Equipment could include a tree stand, however, the height allowed would have to be limited keeping you vulnerable to Utahs and T-Rex.Instead of a red screen at your death, you could show a more animated death from the attacker in a 3rd person view.  And while you wait your 10 seconds you could watch them eat your body.Really Enjoying the game!   Keep up the development, the price is a steal at the early release price, when finished it surely will increase and still be well worth the cost."
