ally would like to. Plus that there is literally 5 dinosaurs right now, the T-rex,velociraptor,Utahraptor,triceratops and the Quetzalcoatlus. You should add more flying reptiles and aquatic dino's such as the Spinosaurus, and maybe the Crocodile. I realize that you can only place dino's that are in the same time era but I have some suggestions for some must have's. The Pachycephalosaurus, Ankylosaurus, Stegasaurus, Brontosaurus and Pentaceratops. A few more random ones I would like are The Giant Sloth, Allosaurus, Iguanodon, Pachyrhinosaurus, Herrerasaurus, Scipionyx, also some omnivores such as the Abrictosaurus, Avimimus, and the Chirostenotes.Now I feel like if you guys updated a lot, and you see what I mean by these paragraphs, that this could be a game everyone loves. But if you flop on it like everyone thinks, someone else will take this awesome idea and make money off it. I'm sure everyone would love if you kept us posted on upcoming updates or things you're working on. Much love and thanks for the read, sincerely an avid fan!"
