ety as well.  After a few hours I've seen all the dinosaurs, seen the one plant that sort of hurts you, and have no interest in playing to see new weapons and equipment.  What's the use of a giant landscape if it's basically the same everywhere?I paid US $30 for this game.  I feel like I've been completely ripped off."
